1️⃣ Scenario: Deploy a Web Server on AWS

Requirement: company wants a simple web server running in AWS.

Task:
Create an EC2 instance
Use Amazon Linux / Ubuntu AMI
Instance type: t2.micro
Allow HTTP (80) and SSH (22) access
Use Terraform variables for region and instance type

Practical Tasks

Write provider.tf
Create aws_instance
Create security_group
Use terraform init, plan, apply
